    "body": "### Neovim version (nvim -v)\r\n\r\n0.8.0-dev+519-g6f6286e4f9\r\n\r\n### Vim (not Nvim) behaves the same?\r\n\r\nno, vim 8.2\r\n\r\n### Operating system/version\r\n\r\nlinux 5.15.19-1-MANJARO\r\n\r\n### Terminal name/version\r\n\r\nalacritty 0.10.1\r\n\r\n### $TERM environment variable\r\n\r\nalacritty\r\n\r\n### Installation\r\n\r\nAUR\r\n\r\n### How to reproduce the issue\r\n\r\n### action 1:\r\n```\r\nnvim --clean\r\n:set virtualedit=onemore\r\n:set showbreak=bbbb\r\ni\r\n<C-r>=repeat('a',&columns)\r\n<esc>l\r\n### action 2:\r\nnvim --clean\r\n:set virtualedit=onemore\r\n:set showbreak=bbbb\r\n:set number\r\ni\r\n<C-r>=repeat('a',&columns-4)\r\n<esc>l\r\n```\r\n\r\n### Expected behavior\r\n\r\neither:\r\naction 1  and action 2 cursor position being at edge\r\nor\r\naction 1  and action 2 cursor position being indented\r\n\r\n### Actual behavior\r\n\r\naction 1 cursor position being at edge\r\naction 2 cursor position being indented",
